data.description:
Discover a world of contemporary elegance blended seamlessly with timeless character in this single-family conversion in the vibrant McKinley Heights neighborhood!

The main floor is a sunlit oasis, boasting an open floorplan that's perfect for entertaining. A bespoke staircase, warm grey engineered flooring, and a show-stopping kitchen take center stage, a feast for the senses. This kitchen features storage galore, a central island, pantry, and a breakfast room that beckons you to the fenced backyard. And then there's the half bath and laundry on the first floor.

Upstairs, you'll find three spacious bedrooms. The primary is a sanctuary, complete with a walk-in closet and a lavish full bath featuring double sinks, a separate tub, and a sleek shower.

Outside, the backyard is beautiful and there's off-street parking for two cars – a rare gem in this desirable neighborhood.
it's time to start living the lifestyle you deserve, book your showing today!
